<p>The tricky part is that when psychopaths are forced to see reality and let go of their illusions, they often have psychotic breaks, and these psychopaths are heavily armed with nuclear weapons. Putin&#8217;s big challenge is to avoid a nuclear war while the US is collapsing in on itself, and keep avoiding that war until after all of the nuclear weapons in the US have become nonfunctional due to lack of parts and competent maintenance. This could take a long time. </p>
