</b><br />
<b>The game:</b> Gain control of a large society by using a small number of military operatives.</p>
<p>Let’s use clandestine military operatives numbering .0001 percent of the targeted society.</p>
<p>100 million times .0001 = 10,000.</p>
<p><b>So 10,000 clandestine military operatives will play this game to win against a society with a population of 100 million.</b></p>
