 us stronger" are valid principles of war, that white hillbillies &amp; white urban ethnics are more likely to be seditious racist terrorists than what they have always been in all our wars: the backbone of our combat forces.  <br /><br />And I have no confidence that even disastrous defeat would cause our leaders to change the "woke mil" to a military which could fight &amp; win, such is the apparent grip of radical egalitarian ideology upon our generals and admirals today.<p/><strong>Replies: @Jatt Aryaa, @Robert Dolan, @Abelard Lindsey</strong></div></span><div  class='comment-text' ><p>Thanks for your info.</p>
