<p>Forgive me if you’ve heard this before &#8211; the smartest is not always the richest, the strongest and the most fit is not always best in battle, the wisest my not live in the most comfort, the most handsome doesn’t always win the pretty girl.<br />
<i>Life is random.</i> </p>
