ionists Dengoids in mainland and the gay taiwanese in the island.<p/>China failed to colonize SEA even when we were tribesmen, they could do jackshit now with when we have developed our own national language.<p/><strong>Replies: @Shortsword, @China Japan and Korea Bromance of Three Kingdoms, @Rattus Norwegius</strong></div></span><div  class='comment-text' ><p>Would you support Chinese ownership of the Paracel islands if China abandoned it&#8217;s claim (justified or not) on the Spratly Islands? Does that seem like a fair compromise? </p>
